    Implement comprehensive remote control support for TV/STB devices
    
    - Add DeviceHelper utility for generic remote detection and input tracking
    - Add FocusManager and FocusIndicator for focus state management
    - Add VirtualKeyboard composable for remote text input (QWERTY layout)
    - Add FileBrowserDialog for remote file selection
    - Add RemoteDialog wrapper for enhanced dialog focus support
    - Update MainActivity with remote key handling (CHANNEL_UP/DOWN, INFO, MENU, number pad)
    - Add focus support to ChannelListItem (DPAD_CENTER=play, DPAD_RIGHT=EPG)
    - Add focus support to EpgProgramItem (DPAD_CENTER=details, DPAD_RIGHT=archive)
    - Add focus support to PlaylistPanel and EpgPanel with auto-scroll
    - Add focus support to CustomControlButtons and ProgramDetailsPanel
    - Update SettingsScreen with remote navigation support
    - Update all dialogs (channel, search, URL input, confirmation) with RemoteDialog
    - Add Russian translations for keyboard and file browser strings
    - Fix compilation errors: Key comparisons, imports, focusable modifiers
    - All UI elements now accessible via D-pad navigation without touch screen

